    "title": "EndingDigitalSlavery"
  }, "EndingDigitalSlavery"), " and otherwise protecting / supporting the human rights of persons, and other related values.  Yet, the available means to do this properly in Australia, has led to difficulties."), mdx("p", null, "In the Commonwealth of Australia, the guiding instument for the governance of most incorporated entities is the ", mdx("a", {
